  "page": "Justice and Injustice in the North: Judgments of Three Stark Lords",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Justice and Injustice in the North: Judgments of Three Stark Lords</b></i> is a book written by <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Egbert\" title=\"Egbert\">Egbert</a>. In the text it is noted that crimes in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> in which <a href=\"/index.php/Guest_right\" title=\"Guest right\">guest right</a> was violated were rare but were invariably treated as harshly by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> as the direst of treasons. Only <a href=\"/index.php/Kinslaying\" title=\"Kinslaying\">kinslaying</a> is deemed as sinful as the violations of these laws of hospitality.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_north.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_north.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Justice_and_Injustice_in_the_North:_Judgments_of_Three_Stark_Lords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_north.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_north.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The North.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 2026040508